netradiant (1.5.0+20220629+1-WIP+REL) stable; urgency=medium

  * Update upstream.
  * Move source files around into ./source-files/.
  * Moved the tools from /usr/bin to to libdir. This way we don't need to
    Conflict with GtkRadiant or NRC (nrcradiant) anymore.
  * TODO: chromium snaps can read in /usr/share/doc, but not in
    /usr/share/*radiant/... So, we should really try to move the docs if
    possible. Otherwise the Jump-to-help doesn't work very well.

 -- Walter Doekes <wjdoekes+netradiant@osso.nl>  Sat, 16 Jul 2022 20:38:00 +0200

